title: Gold Clicker [Arcade, Eng, 2018]
description:
Have you ever wanted to become the richest gold digger in the Wild West? The Texas Valley is waiting for you! With each click, your dream is getting closer and closer.

This is a free game dedicated to clicking and achieving a dream. Gold mining, gold prospecting - it is that will make you trillionaire! Do everything to become the richest! Achieve your dream!

Features:
- Dig gold to earn more and more money.
- Improve your equipment and mining drills.
- Strive to your dream
- Become the richest gold miner!

System:

ОС: Windows 7 +
CPU: 1 GHz
RAM: 128 mb
VRAM: 64 mb
HDD: 58 mb
